      "content": "thanks for that. i guess i'm just wondering if there's a consensus on whether this is actually helping kids or if it's just causing more drama. like, is there any actual evidence that this kind of stuff is necessary for a school, or is it more of a political thing? i'm trying to figure out if the school is actually doing something \"right\" or if they're just following a trend.",
